{"tid":2159232,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰: 【總辭等於不參與選舉】","createTime":"2020-08-16T07:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T10:02:49.000Z","uid":126889,"like":3,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2540244f228eb2d29364558fe22e1fc0c3dad02e","tid":2159232,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:54:23.000Z","msg":"我為人耿直不阿，不厭其煩重申一次：<br />\n<br />\n總辭，我 okie 的，但總辭一年，我理解唔到；<br />\n要總辭，就不再參與選舉，包括各級選舉制度。<br />\n<br />\n因為這才是「攬炒」，是你們琅琅上口地鼓動的；<br />\n整色整水的話，不要我浪費時間，我是辦事的人，沒有閒情逸致學術討論「總辭」的定義，況且香港亦沒有這個時間。"},{"pid":"eee1ebc3425dcdad28aa9a4542438eb235e5377b","tid":2159232,"uid":10398,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"做返自己野 明既"},{"pid":"e43937dc7b1bc2fbe05f15b4b06c6104248d863d","tid":2159232,"uid":251732,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八喺度刷存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d93a1309c456c78b8db1ee3e87a63ad9641032","tid":2159232,"uid":48060,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"有咩做<br />\n趕住調轉支國旗？"},{"pid":"f79e1bcea694dccd0c09d030eb9c3aabc8e134ef","tid":2159232,"uid":18271,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:56:07.000Z","msg":"邊個有預佢"},{"pid":"30043a2965f16f23e89870e98e350b7340916c52","tid":2159232,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:56:09.000Z","msg":"who are u呀？"},{"pid":"2cba87e7539fc143854e1b8555e1ef10854cebea","tid":2159232,"uid":6347,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:56:38.000Z","msg":"david 你唔鍾意咪quit youtube 囉"},{"pid":"c61525ca91a2c36ca5220bd4044e17a5bd99a061","tid":2159232,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:56:46.000Z","msg":"有道理<br />\n政府啲錢點解唔要"},{"pid":"69a5eb3c5c4b0969d8460140fb5c325276e0dbeb","tid":2159232,"uid":120487,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":